public final class EntityComparison
extends ItemComparison

A kind of ItemComparison that represents the differences between two versions of the same Entity.

EntityComparison

public EntityComparison(CoreItem olderItem,
                        CoreItem newerItem,
                        boolean deletionChanged,
                        boolean securityChanged,
                        boolean primaryPropertiesChanged,
                        boolean modifiedTimestampChanged,
                        Collection<String> addedCardIds,
                        Collection<String> removedCardIds,
                        Collection<SourceInfoComparison> changedSourceInfos,
                        Collection<CardComparison> changedCards,
                        Collection<String> addedPropertyGroupIds,
                        Collection<String> removedPropertyGroupIds,
                        Collection<String> addedPropertyIds,
                        Collection<String> removedPropertyIds,
                        Collection<String> changedPropertyIds,
                        boolean altEntityChanged)
Constructs a new EntityComparison.

Parameters:
olderItem - The older Entity in this EntityComparison.
newerItem - The newer Entity in this EntityComparison.
deletionChanged - true if one of the Entity versions is marked as deleted while the other is not; false otherwise.
securityChanged - true if the Entity versions have different security settings; false otherwise.
primaryPropertiesChanged - true if the Entity versions have different primary properties; false otherwise.
modifiedTimestampChanged - true if the Entity versions have different modified timestamps; false otherwise.
addedCardIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the newer but not the older Entity.
removedCardIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the older but not the newer Entity.
changedSourceInfos - SourceInfoComparisons describing SourceInfo changes between Cards present on both Entitys.
changedCards - CardComparisons describing changes between Cards present on both Entitys.
addedPropertyGroupIds - Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the newer but not the older Entity.
removedPropertyGroupIds - Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the older but not the newer Entity.
addedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the newer but not the older Entity.
removedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the older but not the newer Entity.
changedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys whose values are different in the two Entitys.
altEntityChanged - true if the alternative icon URLs are different between the older and newer Entitys; false otherwise.
Method Detail

isAltEntityChanged

public boolean isAltEntityChanged()
Indicates whether the alternative icon URLs are different between the older and newer Entitys in this EntityComparison.

Returns:
true if the alternative icon URLs are different; false otherwise.
